replies.body:
Patches only change local files inside your League directory, so they're **extremely unlikely** to have an impact on your connection. The Mac client, in particular, is pretty sensitive to drops or inconsistencies in connection, and it's likely that there's an issue with local settings or along your route to the server. As a first step, I recommend working through the steps outlined in our [connection troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if those steps caused any change in your issue.
